    "They are therefore at risk of assault and financial fraud inside of this BC.",
    "Furthermore, anonymity makes it difficult to spot irregularities in this vast network.",
    "In Patel et al. (2020), an AD method based on one-class graph Artificial Neural Network (ANN) is proposed and evaluated on the publicly available Ethereum data.",
    "For the purpose of identifying bitcoin malware risks, Yazdinejad et al. (2020a) suggest a deep RNN learning model.",
    "Their method uses the operation codes of Windows apps as an illustration study."
